When 16-year-old Sylvana Hiltrop has to show up for her first day at Tachibana High School, the girls start laughing: the German girl is so kawaii!
What's that supposed to mean?
Sylvana already knows this word thanks to Mangas - in her new Exchange Log, she talks about Japan.
"The first day of school in Japan.
What was I excited about?
Already the way to go to school scared me.
